author: James Ellingworth, Associated Press
title: Massa clocks fastest time in rain-hit 2nd practice in Russia
text: Photo: Ivan Sekretarev, AP Mercedes driver Lewis Hamilton of Britain steers his car during the second free practice at the 'Sochi Autodrom' Formula One circuit in Sochi, Russia, on Friday, Oct. 9, 2015. Mercedes driver Lewis Hamilton of Britain steers his car during the... SOCHI, Russia (AP) — Williams driver Felipe Massa clocked the fastest time in Friday's second practice session for the Russian Grand Prix, with only six other drivers setting times in heavy rain.
